            <title>[SOLR-6206] The migrate collection API fails on retry because temp collection already exists</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6206</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The migrate collection API fails on retry because temp collection already exists. We should attempt to re-use a temp collection after cleaning it up instead of failing the command.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
